tip.text: The Diorama model of KL Malaysia is just AMAZING! Must stop by....
The highest peak you'll have for a 360 view of the whole island... Prepare 200php for the entrance and its better to go there 9am w/c is not to hot for the weather...
If your looking for cheap Filipino food this is where you'll go...PLUS! It near the front beach!
If you got a scrape in your feet this is not advisable activity for you...the experience would be ticklish but once its over you'll see a more cleaner feet! Thank u fishy friends!
They got weird but good "seaweed shaker fries"
You could bring your own lock or you could buy there... Great view perfect for lovers <3 there's also a restaurant just below it...
That huge golden statue! It's a must stop by tourist spot.
